Who is Shanaya Makani?
For International Dance Day, we find out. 🩵

For our next episode of Friends Of Isharya, we spent time with someone who embodies our #HackYourStack mantra. “Bury me with jewellery”, says @shanayamakani , dancer, creator and founder of Beat Studio. She’s goofy, she’s energetic and she’s got a whole lot to say. From chasing the wrong form of self-expression as a career, to the safe spaces she’s created for herself as an artist, she chats with us - cats, dog, macaw et al.

On Shanaya: Villa Isharya & Lolly collections by Isharya. 🌸

#FriendsOfIsharya #InternationalDanceDay

Oh, how I’d kill to be that student walking into the studio for the first time.. clueless, excited, and about to have her whole world changed.
Happy International Dance Day to everyone who finds their peace on the dance floor!
Starting this journey was easily one of the best decisions I’ve ever made. And even though it came with a shit ton of blood, sweat, and tears (literally), I’d do it all over again in a heartbeat♥️
